half of it for $150,000.

00:38:45.845 --> 00:38:47.220
It's almost like
a football game.

00:38:47.220 --> 00:38:49.220
Vince Lombardi once said,
I never lose the game.

00:38:49.220 --> 00:38:50.660
I just run out of time.

00:38:50.660 --> 00:38:52.310
That's very much
the bar business.

00:38:52.310 --> 00:38:54.860
If you just had the money
for another month or two,

00:38:54.860 --> 00:38:57.030
you could've figured
it out and made it.

00:38:57.030 --> 00:38:59.942
And the problem with the bar
business is it's all rookies.

00:38:59.942 --> 00:39:02.400
There's no place where you'd
go and learn the bar business.

00:39:02.400 --> 00:39:03.566
There's hospitality schools.

00:39:03.566 --> 00:39:05.710
There's no bar school.

00:39:05.710 --> 00:39:09.880
So the bar sciences that
I teach-- Google it!

00:39:09.880 --> 00:39:11.844
There's nobody else who
teaches these things.

00:39:11.844 --> 00:39:13.510
There's no other books
with these things

00:39:13.510 --> 00:39:15.180
that teach these sciences.

00:39:15.180 --> 00:39:19.010
So the fact of the matter is I'm
a little unique in what I do,

00:39:19.010 --> 00:39:22.400
but every bar can be
successful, if they just

00:39:22.400 --> 00:39:23.650
changed what they do.

00:39:23.650 --> 00:39:26.280
And I'll leave you with
a quote from, I believe,

00:39:26.280 --> 00:39:27.445
Benjamin Franklin.

00:39:27.445 --> 00:39:29.460
It says "if you do tomorrow,
what you did today,

00:39:29.460 --> 00:39:31.680
you'll get tomorrow
which you got today."

00:39:31.680 --> 00:39:34.150
I got to make them do
something different tomorrow.

00:39:34.150 --> 00:39:35.180
So do they.

00:39:35.180 --> 00:39:37.870
And the strange thing is they
could do that without me.

00:39:37.870 --> 00:39:39.750
But the problem is they
blame the president,

00:39:39.750 --> 00:39:43.370
they blame Congress, they blame
everything else but themselves.

00:39:43.370 --> 00:39:45.440
And then they go home,
mad at somebody else.

00:39:45.440 --> 00:39:48.962
I suggest you should go
home mad at yourself.

00:39:48.962 --> 00:39:50.379
MALE SPEAKER: Great
Next question.

00:39:50.379 --> 00:39:52.878
