and bars worth of data,

00:40:24.580 --> 00:40:27.770
where I've done these
surveys and focus groups.

00:40:27.770 --> 00:40:31.330
So most of this data is owned by
me, really, and created by me.

00:40:31.330 --> 00:40:32.730
It's a little unique.

00:40:32.730 --> 00:40:35.000
And it's not out
there any place else.

00:40:35.000 --> 00:40:37.710
So for me, I know
