00:40:39.580 --> 00:40:41.969
Nobody else has.

00:40:41.969 --> 00:40:43.510
I wish I had a better
answer for you.

00:40:43.510 --> 00:40:45.030
But that's the reality of it to.

00:40:45.030 --> 00:40:47.440
