I have this insatiable
addictive need

00:41:31.230 --> 00:41:33.860
to know what's going
on in your brain.

00:41:33.860 --> 00:41:37.830
So I use every trick in the
book to get to that information.

00:41:37.830 --> 00:41:40.730
So it's 30-year, $60,000
restaurants worth of data.

00:41:40.730 --> 00:41:43.610
It's actually a
really neat database,

00:41:43.610 --> 00:41:47.750
even down to the color of
plates, flow patterns, hours,

00:41:47.750 --> 00:41:50.640
price, points, for example,
psychological pricing.

00:41:50.640 --> 00:41:53.190
And there's no difference
in guest perception

00:41:53.190 --> 00:41:56.010
from $8.25 or $8.95.

00:41:56.010 --> 00:41:57.660
Absolutely zero.

00:41:57.660 --> 00:42:01.890
So if you charge $8.25 instead
of $8.95, you're leaving what?

00:42:01.890 --> 00:42:05.710
60 cents on a table every
time you create a transaction.

00:42:05.710 --> 00:42:08.170
So I can go into a bar, just
change the pricing from $8.50

00:42:08.170 --> 00:42:11.560
to $8.95 on all the menu
items, move some stuff around,

00:42:11.560 --> 00:42:15.360
not change one recipe and
increase revenues by about 20%.

00:42:15.360 --> 00:42:16.710
So that's the science.

00:42:16.710 --> 00:42:19.090
I can box something in
the center of a menu

00:42:19.090 --> 00:42:23.730
and sales of that item will
go up 20% every single time.

00:42:23.730 --> 00:42:25.890
If I bold it, put
Chef's Special on it,

00:42:25.890 --> 00:42:29.590
sales would go up 14% to
17% every single time.

00:42:29.590 --> 00:42:32.340
People have a 6.5%
propensity to order

00:42:32.340 --> 00:42:36.160
the top bottom and bottom two
items on the list on a menu.

00:42:36.160 --> 00:42:37.300
So what am I going to do?

00:42:37.300 --> 00:42:39.140
I'm going to take my
most profitable item,

00:42:39.140 --> 00:42:42.230
box it, shadow it, move it
all around, move it at $8.95,

00:42:42.230 --> 00:42:45.300
and manipulate you to buy
what I'm making money on.

00:42:45.300 --> 00:42:48.170
If there's a menu item
that my customers love,

00:42:48.170 --> 00:42:50.760
that I don't make
money on, I hide it,

00:42:50.760 --> 00:42:53.207
so no new customer find it.

00:42:53.207 --> 00:42:54.540
The old customers know I got it.

00:42:54.540 --> 00:42:55.540
I'm not going to take
it away from you.

00:42:55.540 --> 00:42:57.850
But I don't want anybody else
getting hooked with this thing.

00:42:57.850 --> 00:42:59.058
I want them [CLICKING SOUND].

00:42:59.058 --> 00:43:02.650
So I hide that in the menu, and
move my most profitable items.

00:43:02.650 --> 00:43:04.660
It's incredibly manipulative.

00:43:04.660 --> 00:43:08.471
And I had the confidence to do
this because of that database.

00:43:08.471 --> 00:43:10.220
Or I probably wouldn't
have the confidence

00:43:10.220 --> 00:43:12.410
to make the bold moves
that I do sometimes.

